471
00:32:51,757 --> 00:32:52,524
Okay.

472
00:32:53,058 --> 00:32:53,926
Lass uns gehen.

473
00:32:54,493 --> 00:32:56,228
- Geh zuerst.
- Übrigens...

474
00:32:56,962 --> 00:32:59,465
